            <title type="text">Arch Linux中gdm无法开机启动</title>
            <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://Margaret-Zhang.github.io/posts/gdm_problem/" />
            <id>https://Margaret-Zhang.github.io/posts/gdm_problem/</id>
            <updated>2021-05-03T22:29:32&#43;08:00</updated>
            <published>2021-03-03T22:18:10&#43;08:00</published>
            <author>
                    <name>喂，前面可是地狱啊</name>
                    <uri>https://Margaret-Zhang.github.io</uri>
                    <email>3250127220@qq.com</email>
                    </author>
            <rights>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.zh)</rights><summary type="html">URL: https://bbs.archlinux.org/viewtopic.php?id=256896 问题描述: 启用了gdm服务(systemctl enable gdm)的Arch Linux开机需通过切换tty才能显示登录界面。一开始搜索……</summary>
            
                <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;URL: &lt;a href=&#34;https://bbs.archlinux.org/viewtopic.php?id=256896&#34;&gt;https://bbs.archlinux.org/viewtopic.php?id=256896&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;问题描述: 启用了gdm服务(&lt;code&gt;systemctl enable gdm&lt;/code&gt;)的Arch Linux开机需通过切换tty才能显示登录界面。一开始搜索互联网有人认为是系统熵值(&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;1000&lt;/code&gt;)的问题，但检查系统熵值并不低。GNOME换用sddm登录时，可以正常登录，但是GNOME不支持使用sddm锁定计算机。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;问题解决: 修改gdm服务(&lt;code&gt;/usr/lib/systemd/system/gdm.service&lt;/code&gt;)的属性，在[Service]下添加Type和ExecStartPre及其对应的属性。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;[Unit]
Description=GNOME Display Manager

# replaces the getty
Conflicts=getty@tty1.service
After=getty@tty1.service

# replaces plymouth-quit since it quits plymouth on its own
Conflicts=
After=

# Needs all the dependencies of the services it&#39;s replacing
# pulled from getty@.service and 
# (except for plymouth-quit-wait.service since it waits until
# plymouth is quit, which we do)
After=rc-local.service plymouth-start.service systemd-user-sessions.service

# GDM takes responsibility for stopping plymouth, so if it fails
# for any reason, make sure plymouth still stops
OnFailure=plymouth-quit.service

[Service]
Type=idle #搁置类型
ExecStartPre=/bin/sleep 1 #睡眠1秒
ExecStart=/usr/bin/gdm
KillMode=mixed
Restart=always
IgnoreSIGPIPE=no
BusName=org.gnome.DisplayManager
EnvironmentFile=-/etc/locale.conf
ExecReload=/bin/kill -SIGHUP $MAINPID
KeyringMode=shared

[Install]
Alias=display-manager.service
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</content>
            
            
            
            
            
                
                    
                        
                            
                            
                            
